   "label": "about-business",
   "group": "context",
   "excerpt": "# About Olive Tree Investments\n\n## What We Do\n\nOlive Tree Investments is a multifamily real estate syndication firm operating in Georgia and beyond. We find apartment buildings (15\u201350+ doors), partner with operators and experts, execute value-add renovations, improve operations, raise rents to market, and return profits to our investors. Deal timeline is typically 4\u20136 years, with a refinance event around year 4 and a sale at year 6.\n\n## Revenue Model\n\nInvestors receive preferred returns (up to 6% pref) before the GP takes any profit. After the pref is met, profits split 70% LP / 30% GP. Average projected ROI: 18.21% annually. Investors who stay through refi + sale target a 2.09x equity multi",
